Keep going.

652
01:16:40,304 --> 01:16:42,681
He tried to be a good son
and thought he'd be rewarded.

653
01:16:43,807 --> 01:16:45,892
And then the old man
left everything to his granddaughter.

654
01:16:46,059 --> 01:16:48,645
If Mariko got all that power,
she would dump his ass.

655
01:16:48,812 --> 01:16:49,730
It's true.

656
01:16:49,896 --> 01:16:52,983
Mariko would have never
gone through with the wedding...

657
01:16:53,150 --> 01:16:55,652
not once the will was revealed.

658
01:16:56,403 --> 01:16:57,529
She never took to me.

659
01:16:57,988 --> 01:17:00,824
Oh, really?
A class act like you.

660
01:17:01,491 --> 01:17:04,161
Shingen promised me
a fortune for my help.

661
01:17:05,329 --> 01:17:08,874
