Is that it?

662
01:17:10,000 --> 01:17:12,002
Political careers don't last forever.

663
01:17:12,753 --> 01:17:13,670
That's right.

664
01:17:14,004 --> 01:17:15,839
Wait! Wait! No!

665
01:17:16,006 --> 01:17:18,717
You wanted the truth.
I told you the truth!

666
